%h1
  Listing Information Pages
%ul
  %li Create Information Pages which are accessible to the public (available without logging in).
  %li Links to these pages will appear in the top menu bar.
  %li You can create a tree of pages.

%h4 Special Features
%ul
  %li If you create a page with the slug of `home`, it will become the default homepage for the convention.
  %li If you create a page with the slug of `privacy-policy`, it will appear in the footer.

%table
  %thead
    %tr
      %th Slug (url)
      %th Title
      %th
      %th
      %th
  %tbody
    - @pages.each do |page|
      %tr
        %td= page.slug
        %td= page.title
        %td= link_to 'Show', convention_setup_page_path(page)
        %td= link_to 'Edit', edit_convention_setup_page_path(page)
        %td= link_to 'Delete', [:convention_setup, page], method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' }

= link_to "New Page", new_convention_setup_page_path
